<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ràng wǒ men yī qǐ lái zàn měi zhǔ 迦南1313</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ràng wǒ men yī qǐ lái zàn měi zhǔ ràng wǒ men yī qǐ lái jìng bài zhǔ
 yī tóng fēn xiǎng zhǔ bǎo guì de huà yǔ bǐ cǐ miǎn lì bǐ cǐ zhù fú
 zhǔ xǐ yuè yǔ wǒ men tóng zhù zhǔ de tóng zài shǐ wǒ men fǔ fú
 shòu yā dé zì yóu xiā yǎn dé kàn jiàn yǒu zhǔ tóng zài jiù yǒu lù
 zǒu a xī biān yǒu yī tiáo lù kuài bǎ zhǔ de jiù ēn sā biàn zài gè chù
 zǒu a qián fāng yǒu yī tiáo lù yào bǎ zhǔ míng chuán yáng zài gè chù</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1313</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>